sentence: Wednesday's session closes with the NASDAQ Composite Index at 7,728.97.
The total shares traded for the NASDAQ was over 2.43 billion.
Declining stocks led advancers by 1.62 to 1 ratio.
There were 1198 advancers and 1945 decliners for the day.
On the NASDAQ Stock Exchange 50 stocks reached a 52 week high and 28 those reaching lows totaled.
The most active, advancers, decliners, unusual volume and most active by dollar volume can be monitored intraday on the Most Active Stocks page.
The NASDAQ 100 index closed up .43% for the day; a total of 31.47 points.
Fox Corporation ( FOX ) had the largest percent change down (-4.93%) while Netflix, Inc. ( NFLX ) had the largest percent change gain rising 4.58%.
The Dow Jones index closed down -.55% for the day; a total of -141.71 points.
Goldman Sachs Group, Inc. (The) ( GS ) had the largest percent change down (-3.38%) while Home Depot, Inc. (The) ( HD ) had the largest percent change gain rising 1.07%.
